1. *Lift* je pokvaren. (The *elevator* is broken.)
2. Idemo *liftom* na vrh zgrade. (We're taking the *elevator* to the top floor.)
3. On je *pokupio* stvari u *liftu*. (He *picked up* his things in the *elevator*.)
4. *Liftovima* se prevoze teret u skladištima. (Goods are transported using *elevators* in warehouses.)
5. Potrebno je popraviti *liftarski* mehanizam. (The *elevator* mechanism needs to be repaired.)
6. Stan se nalazi na drugom *liftspratu*. (The apartment is on the second *floor* accessed by *elevator*.)
7. *Liftirati* teret je lakše nego nositi ga stepenicama. (It's easier to *lift* cargo than to carry it up the stairs.)
8. *Liftovati* se mora kada se transportuje velika količina robe. (You have to use *elevators* when transporting large quantities of goods.)
9. *Liftom* je dostupan i podrum. (The basement is also accessible by *elevator*.)
10. Za izgradnju zgrade potrebno je ugraditi kvalitetne *liftove*. (Quality *elevators* need to be installed for building construction.)